{"title":"使用 Parallels 安装 Win11","shareable":true,"id":"guide/tip/mac/parallels/win11","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"启动 Parallels"},{"tag":"text","text":["在首次安装并启动后，Parallels 会自动提示您下载并安装 Windows 11。此时请点击“安装 Windows”。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-request.png","desc":"安装提示","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["此时请耐心等待，Parallels 会自动为您下载 Windows 11。","下载完成后，Parallels 会校验镜像的完整性，并自动开始安装。"]},{"tag":"text","type":"tip","text":["在安装过程中，安装程序以及系统会多次重启，同时伴有安装助手窗口多次黑屏、调整大小的情况，这都是正常的。","请耐心等待，完整的安装过程可能需要 5 - 10 分钟。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-download.png","desc":"下载 Windows 11","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-verify.png","desc":"下载完成后，Parallels 会自动校验镜像完整性","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-1.png","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-2.png","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-3.png","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-4.png","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-5.png","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["安装完成后，Parallels 会醒目的图标提醒您，请单击继续。","至此，Windows 11 系统安装已完成。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/tip/mac/parallels/win11-install-finish.png","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","type":"tip","text":["如果您单击后弹出登录窗口，请参考 Parallels 使用。"],"path":"guide/tip/mac/parallels/usage"}],"time":"2023 年 7 月 16 日 19:41:47"}